  "description": "A sustained dub note at maximum drift, maximum reverb, maximum wow — a journey from the initial attack through layers of tape degradation until all that remains is a distant metallic shimmer of spring reverb and bandpass-narrowed ghosts. Press one key and wait ten minutes.",
