    "revelation": "The most Transcendental OVERDUB preset is not the most complex. It is the one that keeps revealing new information over time.",
    "diagnosis": "Tape Journey is the centerpiece Transcendental preset — all degradation mechanisms at maximum, spring reverb at 0.99 size, delay feedback at 0.78. A single note becomes a sound design session that runs until the tape runs out."
